Tanzania Ex-President Mkapa to Testify in Trial, Citizen Says

-- B y   D a v i d   M a l i n g h a   D o y a
-- 
2011-05-06T07:01:50Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-05-06/tanzania-ex-president-mkapa-to-testify-in-trial-citizen-says.html
Tanzanian ex-President Benjamin Mkapa
will testify in the corruption trial of his former ambassador to
 Italy , Costa Mahalu, The Citizen reported, citing a lawyer it
didn’t name.  The “fraudulent purchase” of embassy premises in  Rome 
cost the government 2.5 billion shillings ($1.6 million), the
Dar es Salaam-based newspaper reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 